ygData.messageBody:
Hehe that was me! I make a beautiful corpse! Sylly crys over a Sylly
corpse00

I had met up wif a big old ogre and he was gonna show me the "good spot"
along the river south of the EK bridge. Well, he could not get a decent
pull to save his skin. We had been zoning constantly and then one time -
whoops! I get et by a big ole gryf. So while loading please wait, I go
upstairs for just a minute and opps! I walk too close to my bedroom and get
charmed by my bed! When I got back to my pc this morning, there I was
staring at the zone wall in the arena, wondering what zone I died in <g> I
tend to do that a lot! Really skews my /played times with those 6 and 8
hour rezones!

Sylly!
